<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AHRAP70A5306016" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Uklanjanje i ugradnja sklopa papučice spojke
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A5306015">Komponente sklopa papučice spojke</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A5306016001" page = "2">
<title>
Uklanjanje
</title>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Uklonite potisnu šipku s papučice spojke. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A5306011"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odspojite konektor prekidača CPP br. 1 (ako je dio opreme) i prekidača CPP br. 2, a zatim uklonite prekidač CPP br. 1 (ako je dio opreme) i prekidač CPP br. 2 sa sklopa papučice spojke, ako je potrebno.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
CPP prekidač br. 1: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A5306001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CPP prekidač br. 2: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A5306003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</s1>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Izvadite sklop papučice spojke iz tijela vozila.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A5306016002" page = "2">
<title>
Ugradnja
</title>
<ptxt>
Obrnite redoslijed postupka uklanjanja imajući na umu sljedeće:
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Pritegnite svaki vijak i maticu propisanim momentom pritezanja. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A5306015"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Nanesite mast na vrh potisne šipke.
</ptxt>
<materials>
<materialitem name = "SUZUKI Silicone Grease" id = "M5C002" uid = "21">
<m-part>
</m-part>
<m-desc>
Mazivo
</m-desc>
<m-number>
99000-25100
</m-number>
<m-name>
SUZUKI silikonska mast
</m-name>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</materialitem>
</materials>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Ako je potrebno dodatno podmazivanje, nanesite mast na propisana mjesta. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A5306015"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<materials>
<materialitem name = "SUZUKI Super Grease E" id = "M5C003" uid = "24">
<m-part>
</m-part>
<m-desc>
Mazivo
</m-desc>
<m-number>
99000-25050
</m-number>
<m-name>
SUZUKI Super Mast E
</m-name>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</materialitem>
</materials>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
